verbose_text: Of the remaining 9 genes, the highest expression of TYMS and DPYD was observed in the right sided colon; the highest expression of GGH and EGFR was noted in the left sided colon; the highest expression of DHFR, FPGS, TOP1 and ERCC1 was noted in the rectosigmoid, whereas TYMP expression was approximately equivalent in the right sided colon and rectum, and higher than that in other locations.
